\c 16
\nb
\v 1 Basebewuletha umtshokotsho kaNkulunkulu, bawumisa phakathi kwethente uDavida ayelimisele wona; basebenikela iminikelo yokutshiswa leminikelo yokuthula phambi kukaNkulunkulu.
\v 2 UDavida eseqedile ukunikela umnikelo wokutshiswa leminikelo yokuthula wababusisa abantu ebizweni leN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 3 Wasesabela wonke umuntu wakoIsrayeli kusukela kowesilisa kuze kube kowesifazana, kwaba ngulowo lalowo isinkwa esisodwa, leqatha lenyama, lesinkwa sezithelo zevini ezonyisiweyo.
\p
\v 4 Wasemisa izikhonzi kumaLevi phambi komtshokotsho weN\nd kosi\nd*, ngitsho ukukhumbula lokubonga lokudumisa iN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli.
\v 5 UAsafi inhloko\x + 6.39.\x*, lowesibili kuye uZekhariya\x + 15.18.\x*, uJeyiyeli, loShemiramothi, loJehiyeli, loMathithiya, loEliyabi, loBhenaya, loObedi-Edoma, loJeyiyeli belezinto zezigubhu zezintambo\x + 15.16.\x* njalo lamachacho\x + 15.16.\x*; uAsafi wasezizwakalisa ngezinsimbi ezincencethayo\x + 15.16.\x*;
\v 6 loBhenaya loJahaziyeli abapristi ngezimpondo njalonjalo phambi komtshokotsho wesivumelwano sikaNkulunkulu\x + 15.24.\x*.
\s Ihubo likaDavida lokubonga
\p
\v 7 Ngalesosikhathi ngalolosuku uDavida wanika kuqala \add lesisihlabelelo\add* ukudumisa iN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 2 Sam. 22.1. 23.1.\x* ngesandla sikaAsafi labafowabo\x + 6.39.\x*:
\p
\v 8 Bongani iN\nd kosi\nd*\x + Hlab. 105.1-15.\x*, libize ibizo layo\x + Isa. 12.4.\x*, lazise phakathi kwabantu izenzo zayo\x + Hlab. 145.11.\x*.
\v 9 Hlabelelani kuyo, liyihubele amahubo, lilandise ngezenzo zayo ezimangalisayo\x + Hlu. 5.10.\x*.
\v 10 Zincomeni ebizweni layo elingcwele, kayithokoze inhliziyo yabo abadinga iN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 11 Dingani iN\nd kosi\nd* lamandla ayo, lidinge ubuso bayo njalonjalo\x + Hlab. 24.6. 27.8.\x*.
\v 12 Khumbulani izimangaliso zayo eyazenzayo\x + Hlab. 77.11. 143.5.\x*, izibonakaliso zayo, lezahlulelo zomlomo wayo\x + Eks. 4.21. 7.3. 11.9,10. Hlab. 78.43.\x*,
\v 13 nzalo kaIsrayeli inceku yayo, bantwana bakaJakobe, abakhethiweyo bayo.
\p
\v 14 IyiN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wethu; izahlulelo zayo zisemhlabeni wonke\x + Isa. 26.9.\x*.
\v 15 Khumbulani isivumelwano sayo kuze kube nininini, ilizwi \add e\add*yalilaya kuzinkulungwane zezizukulwana,
\v 16 eyasenza loAbrahama\x + Gen. 17.2. 22.16. 26.3. 28.13. 35.11. Luka 1.73. Heb. 6.17.\x*, lesifungo sakhe kuIsaka\x + Gen. 17.2. 22.16. 26.3. 28.13. 35.11. Luka 1.73. Heb. 6.17.\x*,
\v 17 eyasiqinisa lakuJakobe saba yisimiso, kuIsrayeli saba yisivumelwano esilaphakade,
\v 18 isithi: Ngizakunika ilizwe leKhanani, inkatho yelifa lakho\x + Gen. 13.15. 15.18-21.\x*.
\p
\v 19 Lapho lalibalutshwana ngenani, yebo libalutshwana\x + Dute. 7.7. 26.5.\x*, njalo liyizihambi kulo\x + Heb. 11.9.\x*.
\v 20 Basebezula besuka esizweni besiya esizweni, besuka embusweni besiya kwabanye abantu.
\v 21 Kayivumelanga muntu ukubacindezela\x + Gen. 35.5.\x*; yebo yakhuza amakhosi ngenxa yabo\x + Gen. 12.17. 20.3.\x*:
\v 22 Lingathinti abagcotshiweyo bami, lingoni abaprofethi bami\x + Gen. 20.7.\x*.
\p
\v 23 Hlabelelani eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, mhlaba wonke, litshumayele insuku ngensuku usindiso lwayo\x + Hlab. 96.1-13.\x*.
\v 24 Landisani udumo lwayo phakathi kwezizwe, izimangaliso zayo phakathi kwabantu bonke.
\v 25 Ngoba yinkulu iN\nd kosi\nd*, ifanele ukudunyiswa kakhulu\x + Hlab. 145.3. 2 Sam. 22.4.\x*, iyesabeka phezu kwabonkulunkulu bonke\x + Hlab. 95.3.\x*.
\v 26 Ngoba bonke onkulunkulu bezizwe bayizithombe\x + Levi 19.4.\x*; kodwa iN\nd kosi\nd* yenza amazulu\x + Hlab. 115.15. Isa. 42.5. 44.24. Jer. 10.11,12.\x*.
\v 27 Udumo lenkazimulo kuphambi kwayo, amandla lentokozo kusendaweni yayo\x + Ezra 6.16. Neh. 8.10.\x*.
\v 28 Inikeni iN\nd kosi\nd*, zizukulwana zezizwe, inikeni iN\nd kosi\nd* udumo lamandla\x + Hlab. 29.1.\x*.
\v 29 Inikeni iN\nd kosi\nd* udumo lwebizo layo\x + Hlab. 29.2.\x*, lethani umnikelo lize phambi kwayo. Ikhonzeni iN\nd kosi\nd* ebuhleni bobungcwele\x + 2 Lan. 20.21. Hlab. 29.2. Hlab. 110.3. Zaga 14.28. Hlab. 96. 9.\x*.
\v 30 Lithuthumele phambi kwayo, mhlaba wonke; njalo umhlaba uzaqiniswa, kawuyikunyikinyeka.
\p
\v 31 Kawathokoze amazulu, lomhlaba ujabule\x + Isa. 49.13.\x*, kabatsho phakathi kwezizwe \add ukuthi\add*: IN\nd kosi\nd* iyabusa\x + Hlab. 93.1. 97.1. 99.1. Isa. 52.7. Isam. 11.15,17. 19.6.\x*.
\v 32 Kaluhlokome ulwandle lokugcwala kwalo, iganga kalithabe lakho konke okukulo\x + Hlab. 98.7.\x*.
\v 33 Khona zizahlabelela ngentokozo izihlahla zehlathi phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*, ngoba iyeza ukwahlulela umhlaba.
\p
\v 34 Bongani iN\nd kosi\nd* ngoba ilungile, ngoba umusa wayo \add umi\add* kuze kube phakade\x + 16.41. Hlab. 106.1. 107.1. 118.1. 136.1.\x*.
\v 35 Lithi futhi: Sisindise, Nkulunkulu wosindiso lwethu, usibuthe usikhulule ezizweni, ukuze sibonge ibizo lakho elingcwele, sizincome kudumo lwakho\x + Hlab. 106.47,48.\x*.
\p
\v 36 Kayibusiswe iN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli, kusukela phakade kuze kube phakade\x + Hlab. 41.13.\x*. Bonke abantu basebesithi: Ameni. Basebeyidumisa iN\nd kosi\nd*\x + Dute. 27.15.\x*.
\s Labo abakhethelwa ukulondoloza umtshokotsho wesivumelwano
\p
\v 37 Wasetshiya lapho phambi komtshokotsho wesivumelwano seN\nd kosi\nd* oAsafi labafowabo ukukhonza phambi komtshokotsho njalonjalo\x + 16.4,5.\x* njengodaba losuku ngosuku lwalo\x + 2 Lan. 31.16.\x*.
\v 38 LoObedi-Edoma kanye labafowabo, abangamatshumi ayisithupha lesificaminwembili; uObedi-Edoma indodana kaJeduthuni loHosa babengabagcini bamasango\x + 26.10.\x*.
\v 39 LoZadoki umpristi labafowabo abapristi\x + 15.11.\x* phambi kwethabhanekele leN\nd kosi\nd* endaweni ephakemeyo eyayiseGibeyoni\x + 1 Kho. 3.4.\x*,
\v 40 ukuze banikele iminikelo yokutshiswa eN\nd kosi\nd*ni phezu kwelathi lomnikelo wokutshiswa\x + Eks. 27.1.\x* njalonjalo ekuseni lakusihlwa, lanjengakho konke okubhaliweyo emlayweni weN\nd kosi\nd*, eyawulaya uIsrayeli\x + Eks. 29.38,39,41. Nani 28.3,4.\x*.
\v 41 Njalo kanye labo oHemani\x + 6.33.\x* loJeduthuni\x + 16.38,42. 6.44. 25.1,3,6. 2 Lan. 29.14.\x* labanye ababekhethiwe abamiswa ngamabizo ukubonga iN\nd kosi\nd*\x + Nani 1.17.\x*, ngoba umusa wayo \add umi\add* kuze kube phakade\x + 16.34. 2 Lan. 5.13. 7.3,6. 20.21. Ezra 3.11. Jer. 33.11.\x*.
\v 42 Njalo kanye labo oHemani\x + 6.33.\x* loJeduthuni\x + 38,42. 6.44. 25.1,3,6. 2 Lan. 29.14.\x* babe\add le\add*zimpondo lezinsimbi ezincencethayo\x + 2 Lan. 5.13.\x* zalabo abazizwakalisayo, lezinto zokuhlabelela zikaNkulunkulu\x + 2 Lan. 5.13.\x*. Lamadodana kaJeduthuni ayesesangweni\x + 16.38.\x*.
\v 43 Basebehamba bonke abantu, ngulowo lalowo waya endlini yakhe. UDavida wasebuyela ukubusisa indlu yakhe\x + 2 Sam. 6.19,20.\x*.